name: VentureOutNY
tag_list: ny-tech, nonprofit, international, demo, demo-day, global, brian-frumberg, venture-out, international-startups, international-tech, global-focus
overview: VentureOutNY is focused on helping to enable international startups to launch and succeed in New York City. Based on the philosophy that talent is evenly distributed but opportunity is not, VentureOutNY’s mission is to bridge that gap between the entrepreneurial talent abroad to the vast opportunities in burgeoning technology community in New York. Through regionally focused events, VentureOutNY introduces the world’s most talented international entrepreneurs to the startup ecosystem in NYC, fast tracking their growth by helping establish relationships with the most relevant investors, entrepreneurs and partners in New York City. VentureOutNY was founded by Brian Frumberg in 2011.
